quest'ultima e dell'Org. intern. del lavoro a Ginevra. Fu console onorario del Belgio."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q28196429", "itemLabel": "John Gignoux", "dhsid": "006821", "namefr": "John Gignoux", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Gignoux", "namede": "", "articlede": "", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "102071798X"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q28196429", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/006821/2008-03-17"}